  "text": "In order to make Modbus to be suitable for transmission in the TCP/IP network, Modbus/TCP message format extends some data structure on the basis of the Modbus protocol. As shown in Figure 2 , the Modbus/TCP packet format [CITATION_1] mainly includes three parts: MBAP packet header, Modbus function code, and data.",
